title: Meghan O'Neil from Super Unison and Punch
itunes:title: Meghan O'Neil from Super Unison and Punch
description:
Episode 225 - Meghan O'Neil from Super Unison and Punch is gracing us with her podcast presence today. It was an absolute pleasure having her on the show to discuss being the “team mom”, coming from a musical family and evolving as a person. She’s incredibly insightful, the bands she’s played in are all incredible…what more could you want? Sit back, relax and enjoy this lengthy conversation. Consider being a Bone Marrow donor, like me.
